!
! boot system flash:/vEOS-lab.swi

!
transceiver qsfp default-mode 4x10G
!
service routing protocols model ribd
!
hostname RegionA-CE01
!
spanning-tree mode mstp
!
vlan 10,20,110,120
!
vrf instance vrf1
!
management api http-commands
   protocol unix-socket
   no shutdown
!
interface Port-Channel1
   load-interval 30
   no switchport
   ip address 172.16.5.1/30
   ipv6 address fc00:172:16:5::1/64
   port-channel min-links 1
!
interface Port-Channel2
   load-interval 30
   switchport trunk allowed vlan 10,110
   switchport mode trunk
   port-channel min-links 1
!
interface Port-Channel3
   load-interval 30
   switchport trunk allowed vlan 20,120
   switchport mode trunk
   port-channel min-links 1
!
interface Ethernet1
   no switchport
   ip address 172.16.1.2/30
   ipv6 enable
   ipv6 address fc00:172:16:1::2/64
   ipv6 ospf 1 area 0.0.0.0
!
interface Ethernet2
   no switchport
   ip address 172.16.3.2/30
   ipv6 enable
   ipv6 address fc00:172:16:3::2/64
   ipv6 ospf 1 area 0.0.0.0
!
interface Ethernet3
   load-interval 30
   speed forced 1000full
   channel-group 1 mode active
!
interface Ethernet4
   load-interval 30
   speed forced 1000full
   channel-group 1 mode active
!
interface Ethernet5
   load-interval 30
   speed forced 1000full
   switchport trunk allowed vlan 10,110
   switchport mode trunk
   channel-group 2 mode active
!
interface Ethernet6
   load-interval 30
   speed forced 1000full
   switchport trunk allowed vlan 10,110
   switchport mode trunk
   channel-group 2 mode active
!
interface Ethernet7
   load-interval 30
   speed forced 1000full
   switchport trunk allowed vlan 20,120
   switchport mode trunk
   channel-group 3 mode active
!
interface Ethernet8
   load-interval 30
   speed forced 1000full
   switchport trunk allowed vlan 20,120
   switchport mode trunk
   channel-group 3 mode active
!
interface Ethernet9
!
interface Ethernet10
!
interface Ethernet11
!
interface Ethernet12
!
interface Ethernet13
!
interface Ethernet14
!
interface Ethernet15
!
interface Ethernet16
!
interface Ethernet17
!
interface Ethernet18
!
interface Ethernet19
!
interface Management1
   speed 10full
   ip address 10.0.0.15/24
   ipv6 enable
   ipv6 address auto-config
   ipv6 nd ra rx accept default-route
!
interface Vlan10
   ip address 172.30.10.1/24
   ipv6 address fc00:172:30:10::1/64
   vrrp 1 priority-level 110
   vrrp 1 ipv4 172.30.10.3
   vrrp 1 ipv6 fc00:172:30:10::3
!
interface Vlan20
   ip address 172.30.20.1/24
   ipv6 address fc00:172:30:20::1/64
   vrrp 1 priority-level 110
   vrrp 1 ipv4 172.30.20.3
   vrrp 1 ipv6 fc00:172:30:20::3
!
interface Vlan110
   vrf vrf1
   ip address 172.30.110.1/24
   ipv6 address fc00:172:30:110::1/64
   vrrp 1 priority-level 110
   vrrp 1 ipv4 172.30.110.3
   vrrp 1 ipv6 fc00:172:30:110::3
!
interface Vlan120
   vrf vrf1
   ip address 172.30.120.1/24
   ipv6 address fc00:172:30:120::1/64
   vrrp 1 priority-level 110
   vrrp 1 ipv4 172.30.120.3
   vrrp 1 ipv6 fc00:172:30:120::3
!
ip routing ipv6 interfaces 
ip routing vrf vrf1
!
ipv6 unicast-routing
!
router ospf 1
   router-id 1.1.1.3
   passive-interface default
   no passive-interface Ethernet1
   no passive-interface Ethernet2
   network 0.0.0.0/0 area 0.0.0.0
   max-lsa 12000
!
ipv6 router ospf 1
   router-id 1.1.1.3
!
